name: Scarlet Humanoid
description:
#2 of 6 from Meta Filipina Collection. 

In collaboration with ohhhhhhhmae, we wanted to create a collection through our experiences during quarantine. I had a fascination with how we are mislead in leadership. This was a journey in “finding beauty” through dense places. With my love of color, energy of the Aries, and something floral, Scarlet Humanoid was born.
